{"tid":372571,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（食過煙嘅入嚟）你哋戒煙嘅原因係咩？","createTime":"2017-08-24T11:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T10:41:34.000Z","uid":8106,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"884866a1e5ed9b4231b7301e706f03b3e7a7829c","tid":372571,"uid":8106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"如題，你哋戒煙嘅原因係咩？"},{"pid":"27fd0ab972a4fa573fe4cee22b4d71e20aad5b6e","tid":372571,"uid":8106,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:51:42.000Z","msg":"我諗咗好耐 都未搵到自己要為咩戒煙"},{"pid":"93f11d85d617a038be7a7edb1daa93305bb98384","tid":372571,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"忙住含撚"},{"pid":"9fe7ff828f66365c44ca5d400438ced8382e2f60","tid":372571,"uid":86175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:54:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗咗好耐 都未搵到自己要為咩戒煙</blockquote>我都諗咗好耐 你做乜要食煙"},{"pid":"d6c8b4b20de0ae4ceb6a1e42a2fefcdc37f55135","tid":372571,"uid":8106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12aa1b6563db2e51e452059552239813b8fc4400","tid":372571,"uid":8106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>忙住含撚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係gay㗎"},{"pid":"4e455700b6c301fa49ab56fd0e3a7e744aa62690","tid":372571,"uid":21488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"食得耐會發覺食黎無咩謂 之後有諗過戒<br />\n但食飽飯同柯屎仲有同朋友出街真係最難頂<br />\n結果又係食番"},{"pid":"630da5a357a2bdec37968ec04de6a8bc39cca021","tid":372571,"uid":48165,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:27:10.000Z","msg":"次次戒都係為咗女仔 唔知點解追親或者熟嘅都唔鍾意我食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我keep住食煙嘅原因係因為我有抑鬱、日日厭世嘅時候得呢樣嘢陪住我，或者叫做我選擇咗佢 因為佢唔會同我講嘢唔會講我唔想聽嘅嘢，而且呼出嚟嗰吓其實真係好 舒壓。"},{"pid":"362837a7d11198cffafa79dfc266b12bccae3bac","tid":372571,"uid":8106,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食得耐會發覺食黎無咩謂 之後有諗過戒<br />\n但食飽飯同柯屎仲有同朋友出街真係最難頂<br />\n結果又係食番</blockquote><br />\n所以其實食煙係咪一定唔好？<br />\n我覺得係一種生活態度嚟<br />\n最緊要自己要識享受 enjoy."},{"pid":"daa657850876cfe01d0062fbdabbfb6fac8290ad","tid":372571,"uid":8106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次戒都係為咗女仔 唔知點解追親或者熟嘅都唔鍾意我食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我keep住食煙嘅原因係因為我有抑鬱、日日厭世嘅時候得呢樣嘢陪住我，或者叫做我選擇咗佢 因為佢唔會同我講嘢唔會講我唔想聽嘅嘢，而且呼出嚟嗰吓其實真係好 舒壓。</blockquote><br />\n既然係咁 我覺得就無咩必要去戒<br />\n我自己都覺得 其實無理由為女人去戒<br />\n唔通分咗手又好 點都好之後又因爲佢而食返咩<br />\n最緊要睇自己點睇"},{"pid":"a2b0471a1eaf26d9347f8f994a3d6a5d44c798b0","tid":372571,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"大壓力個陣食一兩支，冇咩事就唔食"},{"pid":"30e033b9be63ce4edeee5db963f9614a6fd483eb","tid":372571,"uid":8106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大壓力個陣食一兩支，冇咩事就唔食</blockquote><br />\n有無癮先覺得自己"},{"pid":"895e1406a0344e098c9a3be37b83499eb7f84281","tid":372571,"uid":91497,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你吸左d煙落個肺，壓力就會細左，咁搞笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f987c841c03d055644893c13872c63ba6597a5c","tid":372571,"uid":32836,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"一切咩舒壓都假既<br />\n食完咪嗰幾分鐘好似好舒服咁 根本就無解決過咩野 <br />\n只係化學物質令到你個大腦繼而影響個情緒 <br />\n令到個人覺得好爽好舒壓<br />\n過返一頭半粒鐘d癮又黎又扯返飛<br />\n成件事就係慢性自殺<br />\n我覺得係個思維既問題<br />\n<br />\n利申：戒左"},{"pid":"df2bef5af7d41eea9cd6fc39cf2184517aa24df6","tid":372571,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大壓力個陣食一兩支，冇咩事就唔食</blockquote><br />\n有無癮先覺得自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反酒我就覺得自己有上癮<br />\n唔飲就身痕"},{"pid":"7259b8a7f4267acc9d1b826714d70bf78c00266b","tid":372571,"uid":138184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:02:25.000Z","msg":"食煙既人個腦裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9374436c15e2f87a4d6b3522146714d97842e568","tid":372571,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題，你哋戒煙嘅原因係咩？</blockquote><br />\nEx叫我戒 最後戒左三個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b27b6258006cdf979c1c960b31243f0c677597","tid":372571,"uid":8106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T19:13:14.000Z","msg":"我已經稔唔透我為咩戒"},{"pid":"f581446c194d7657de0d8a93f8a527555aeed51a","tid":372571,"uid":140001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T19:21:51.000Z","msg":"原本諗住自己食冇乜所謂<br />\n但慢慢搞到身邊啲人跟住食 <br />\n利申冇導佢地食我至撚憎導人食煙的人<br />\n覺得佢地好似因為我係到作賤自己咁<br />\n為試而試 又覺得冇乜野所以keep住食<br />\n但其實真係好無謂<br />\nM9k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反思番自己都係咁ge心態<br />\n於是我好想戒左呢個垃圾佢<br />\n不再害人"},{"pid":"52901561da33eed62d96dffa6632d451b47a7365","tid":372571,"uid":133038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T19:37:30.000Z","msg":"窮"},{"pid":"a12154ed5c69deab52368519085db9e7a9f8e860","tid":372571,"uid":63648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T19:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3967a5ccf016096cb951000cc62f6d0e90b13bf8","tid":372571,"uid":74652,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T21:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a1bb32d841c72dbb455a42653d85068e95fcf5","tid":372571,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T21:27:48.000Z","msg":"形象<br />\n唔想依賴"},{"pid":"92ff4b56bf283f546694a0f6ebf317f5d11c392b","tid":372571,"uid":125499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T22:07:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你吸左d煙落個肺，壓力就會細左，咁搞笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼古丁可以舒緩緊張情架"},{"pid":"0439440e1889468cc0268bf0bf8beba14dd0c27e","tid":372571,"uid":125499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T22:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你吸左d煙落個肺，壓力就會細左，咁搞笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼古丁可以舒緩緊張情架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n緒"},{"pid":"16e66c32cafecc2c8e754f4f79ad0965601a9c63","tid":372571,"uid":131962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T00:56:34.000Z","msg":"戒唔到<br />\n個人太緊張<br />\n寧願食煙都唔想食藥"},{"pid":"304d74fc6ed15294e1c4cfb353e4622c5e1ae4e8","tid":372571,"uid":139592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"自己係運動員 所以戒"},{"pid":"88dad551a6a5a88483ad86bfbfd99f6c6f494822","tid":372571,"uid":139483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T02:40:36.000Z","msg":"身體問題，之前咳到成日訓唔到，而家戒緊，冇咳得咁勁，而家連酒都冇飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6308997957fb429e2082caa5bd8e1cff2b04ae","tid":372571,"uid":131962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身體問題，之前咳到成日訓唔到，而家戒緊，冇咳得咁勁，而家連酒都冇飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947cf5d674d70feb99498ec579492c00c228cec3","tid":372571,"uid":72567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T02:53:00.000Z","msg":"覺得食煙好撚無謂<br />\n要放鬆/whatever ，有其他更好嘅方法<br />\n無必要一定要靠食煙<br />\n心癮習慣左姐，有一日唔想再食就無再食了<br />\n但自此，野飲不離手"},{"pid":"7ec77ca28b97afe31daef2e7132b610865c27ada","tid":372571,"uid":139483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>身體問題，之前咳到成日訓唔到，而家戒緊，冇咳得咁勁，而家連酒都冇飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靠自己意志，唔夜訓，就咁戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576e7a4a43ed89b641c7a87abce97c1479308aca","tid":372571,"uid":131962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>身體問題，之前咳到成日訓唔到，而家戒緊，冇咳得咁勁，而家連酒都冇飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靠自己意志，唔夜訓，就咁戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔夜訓都戒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係成日返屋企既時候係樓下食..."},{"pid":"624a405d521f3a864b474c23d93b4aef059d60d9","tid":372571,"uid":88190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗咗好耐 都未搵到自己要為咩戒煙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講煙對身體唔好就大家都知，如果戒咗，你心情唔好，又會想食，所以最重要係你諗到方法去放鬆，去減壓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2de5942198215c242c5242d2f7f11f8df00040","tid":372571,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己係運動員 所以戒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩個真，食煙對氣管真係差啲，我啲運動員朋友都唔想影響所以戒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09596276b0896212c6701b13d31e73141463f4b4","tid":372571,"uid":139483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>身體問題，之前咳到成日訓唔到，而家戒緊，冇咳得咁勁，而家連酒都冇飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靠自己意志，唔夜訓，就咁戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔夜訓都戒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係成日返屋企既時候係樓下食...</blockquote><br />\n或者咁講啦，同自己講唔好落bar,去蒲,第一日係最難頂，想食煙就深呼吸，過左第一日已經成功左第一步，之後keep 住一個禮拜，你已經冇咁大煙癮，過到一個月基極產連心癮都戒埋，不過我自己都keep唔飲酒,費事放鬆左又食返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fad1ecffd759c9e597bb25a6aa3cee3de907945","tid":372571,"uid":20654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"好老實<br />\n冇錢"},{"pid":"c3558fa846e2327fd6623c1c023593dace1ae7e2","tid":372571,"uid":14885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T08:39:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好老實<br />\n冇錢</blockquote><br />\n好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1039b4c318564885ffb5b6c4baa6fe49e0b46c5","tid":372571,"uid":68732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:22:34.000Z","msg":"小弟從事設計行業 所以好多時有壓力又成日通頂 夜晚真係冇煙冇精神<br />\n不過戒過兩次煙 1次女朋友唔鍾意 <br />\n1次記係做運動發覺心肺差左（不過後尾發覺食煙條氣仲順d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只係作息唔定時又少做運動先差）"},{"pid":"e1394cf4ec133b7145a408247facc86f693e6c46","tid":372571,"uid":68732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟從事設計行業 所以好多時有壓力又成日通頂 夜晚真係冇煙冇精神<br />\n不過戒過兩次煙 1次女朋友唔鍾意 <br />\n1次記係做運動發覺心肺差左（不過後尾發覺食煙條氣仲順d<img src=\"/as